  "texts": [
    "Our review is by no means exhaustive, but aims to highlight the scientific challenges in the fields of thermodynamics, fluid dynamics, and structural mechanics, and more importantly, their nonlinear couplings, that are open.",
    "The solution to these challenges would lead to new and more capable technologies.",
    "In a nutshell, the synergies between scientific and technological exploration strategies for deep space exploration promise to open new horizons of research.",
